# Dispatcharr String Resources (English)

# Category labels
30000=General
30001=Connection Settings
30002=Catchup Settings

# Connection Setting Labels
30010=Backend URL
30011=The base URL of your Dispatcharr middleware instance (e.g., http://localhost:9191)
30012=Username
30013=Your Dispatcharr account username
30014=Password
30015=Your Dispatcharr account password
30016=API Token
30017=JWT API token (optional, auto-populated after login)

# Catchup Settings
30018=Catchup Window (Days)
30019=Number of days of catchup data to support (1-30 days)
